Step 1: Optical Table Assembly
1. Assemble vibration-isolated optical table (Newport RS-4000 or equivalent)
2. Level table to <0.1° using precision level
3. Mount breadboard on vibration isolators

Step 2: Laser System Installation
1. Mount 532nm laser on optical post
2. Install optical isolator (30dB minimum isolation)
3. Align beam to table height (typically 4.5")
4. Install beam expander (3x) for uniform illumination
